{
  "stem": "15991.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the rumors you hear, which you'd-- you believe, but you didn't really know whether they were true.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not as far as I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If there were, I did not attend them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, we were really-- it was being herded into one place, and kept their isolated from the rest, just in case we could be dangerous.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were together with spies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were people there who were known spies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Luckily, they were in the hotels, so we had nothing to do with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is something that was talked about a lot, that there were people who really belonged there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But a lot of people didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- yes?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one day when we were allowed to meet the men-- relatives, friends, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was so badly organized that when I arrived, wherever we were supposed to meet them, my father was not there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was interned also.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never met him there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was released after about four months, due to my mother having said that she was not well, and she needed me at home.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very much needed there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was one reason-- one way I could get released.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was a nice-- nice feeling to be able to come home and not have one's freedom curbed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was really the first time that I had felt what it's like not to be able to go do what you want to do.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But under really very mild circumstances.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "16.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wanting to be free, worried about the family, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] yes, a lot of worries-- worried about the rumors that you heard, worried about what would happen to you, oneself.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
